[{"date":"1954-12-29","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/43/8c/112687_71S1A.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/43/8c/112687_71S1A.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/43/8c/112687_71S1A.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/43/8c/112687_71S1A.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/43/8c/112687_71S1A.jpg"},"summary":"在一个农场内，饲养着各种牲畜，它们都是农场主人的私有财产，等待他们的只有一生劳动以及最后被卖掉和被吃掉的下场。农场里的一头猪在提出了“人类剥削牲畜，牲畜须革命”的理论之后死去，不久农场便掀起了一场由猪领导的革命，原来的剥削者──农场主被赶走，牲畜们实现了“当家作主”的愿望，尝到了革命果实的甘美，农场更名为“动物农场”并且制定了农场的宪法── 七诫。 \r\n但是不久，作为领导革命的猪们内部发生了分裂，一头猪被宣布为革命的敌人。此后，获取了领导权的猪拥有了越来越大的权力和越来越多的特别待遇，逐渐脱离了其他动物，最终蜕变成为和人类完全一样的牲畜剥削者，动物农场的名字也被放弃。 \r\n本片乔治·奥威尔（George Orwell）1945年出版的同名小说《动物农庄》改编，同时是英国第一部影院动画电影长片。","name":"Animal Farm","name_cn":"动物农场","tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":40,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":38,"total_cont":0},{"name":"小说改","count":29,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画电影","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"文学改编","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1954","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动物庄园","count":15,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1950s","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"英国","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Society","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Politics","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"讽刺","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"20世纪","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美漫","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"政治","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"寓言","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"JohnHalas","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"非日本动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"其他星人","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧情","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2025","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"历史","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"黑暗","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Dystopia","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1980年前","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Film","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Animation","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"fantasy","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"JoyBatchelor",